title: Fist of the north star Epiodes 1-109
description:
The entire Fist of the North Star series one, there was a second series that ran for 32 episodes, but wasn't half as good (apparently).

Japanese speech with English hard subtitles.

I tracked these episodes down on the internet and through existing torrents, I also chopped the opening sequence and ending credits from every episode except the first to save quite a bit of space.

Also included is the original movie which is dubbed into English.

I'm hoping there are some people out there who would like to watch and share this, it can be a pain to find all the episodes online.

Episode 96 is missing because I couldn't find it. If anyone knows where to get it could they please let me know.

My upload speeds aren't all that great, I will try to concentrate most of it for this torrent for a while in the hope of it becoming popular.
